To list all socker conatiners-
docker ps -a

To list all dpcker images-
docker images

To check docker version-
docker --version

To restart and start docker container-
docker start/restart <container name/container ID>

To stop docker container-
docker stop <container name/container ID>

To remove docker container-
docker rm <container name/container id>

To remove docker image -
docker rmi <image name/image ID>

To get metadata of docker image/container-
docker inspect <container name/imgae name>

For some specific info like ip address-

docker inspect -f {{ip address}}

To build a docker container-
docker run -it --name <container name> <image name>

To build a docker image using Jenkinsfile-
docker build -t <cutomize image name> <docker file location>
